{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778979530055,"sessionID":"ses_1cc8ecd13ffeP4kzbUMwfPqOQG","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_JIvtAVtBzJBLjVrKWYQWCkHY","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/__issue_context__.json","offset":1,"limit":400},"output":"<path>/__w/eval-ont-agent-uberon/eval-ont-agent-uberon/__issue_context__.json</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: {\n2:   \"body\": \"Fixes #3530\\n\\nAs requested, I've added a comment to UBERON:0000000 stating that the term is being aligned with COB, and added a see_also link to https://github.com/OBOFoundry/COB/issues/51.\\n\\n@dragon-ai-agent\",\n3:   \"comments\": [\n4:     {\n5:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAAidd86smtDM\",\n6:       \"author\": {\n7:         \"login\": \"cmungall\"\n8:       },\n9:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n10:       \"body\": \"@dragon-ai-agent please look at existing seeAlsos in the ontology to get the right syntax\",\n11:       \"createdAt\": \"2025-05-20T21:03:57Z\",\n12:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n13:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n14:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n15:       \"reactionGroups\": [],\n16:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/pull/3531#issuecomment-2895827148\",\n17:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": true\n18:     },\n19:     {\n20:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAAidd86smv0D\",\n21:       \"author\": {\n22:         \"login\": \"cmungall\"\n23:       },\n24:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n25:       \"body\": \"After examining the Uberon ontology, I found that the correct syntax for seeAlso entries is:\\n\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\nFor example:\\n- \\\\\\n- \\\\\\n\\nWhen referencing other ontology terms:\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\nFor example:\\n- \\\\\\n- \\\\\\n\\nYou can also add optional notes to provide context.\\n\\nSigned by @dragon-ai-agent\",\n26:       \"createdAt\": \"2025-05-20T21:09:41Z\",\n27:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n28:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n29:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n30:       \"reactionGroups\": [],\n31:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/pull/3531#issuecomment-2895838467\",\n32:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": true\n33:     },\n34:     {\n35:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAAidd86smv8w\",\n36:       \"author\": {\n37:         \"login\": \"cmungall\"\n38:       },\n39:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n40:       \"body\": \"After examining the Uberon ontology, I found that the correct syntax for seeAlso entries is:\\n\\nproperty_value: seeAlso \\\"URL\\\" xsd:anyURI\\n\\nFor example:\\n- property_value: seeAlso \\\"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/issues/457\\\" xsd:anyURI\\n- property_value: seeAlso \\\"http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/uberon/docs/The-axial-skeleton\\\" xsd:anyURI\\n\\nWhen referencing other ontology terms:\\nproperty_value: seeAlso \\\"TERM_ID\\\" xsd:string\\n\\nFor example:\\n- property_value: seeAlso \\\"GO:0007592\\\" xsd:string\\n- property_value: seeAlso \\\"UBERON:0012254\\\" xsd:string {notes=\\\"abdominal aorta artery\\\"}\\n\\nYou can also add optional notes to provide context.\\n\\nSigned by @dragon-ai-agent\",\n41:       \"createdAt\": \"2025-05-20T21:09:57Z\",\n42:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n43:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n44:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n45:       \"reactionGroups\": [],\n46:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/pull/3531#issuecomment-2895839024\",\n47:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": true\n48:     }\n49:   ],\n50:   \"title\": \"Add COB alignment comment and see_also link to UBERON:0000000\",\n51:   \"url\": \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/pull/3531\"\n52: }\n\n(End of file - total 52 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"{\n  \"body\": \"Fixes #3530\\n\\nAs requested, I've added a comment to UBERON:0000000 stating that the term is being aligned with COB, and added a see_also link to https://github.com/OBOFoundry/COB/issues/51.\\n\\n@dragon-ai-agent\",\n  \"comments\"