{"type":"text","timestamp":1778979538166,"sessionID":"ses_1cc8ecd13ffeP4kzbUMwfPqOQG","part":{"id":"prt_e33717654001gAOQBxagmR3czu","messageID":"msg_e33716616001xANr5DYyeadlOw","sessionID":"ses_1cc8ecd13ffeP4kzbUMwfPqOQG","type":"text","text":"The imported context is clear: this is a small follow-up fix for `UBERON:0000000`, specifically correcting the `seeAlso` syntax to match existing ontology usage while keeping the COB alignment note. Next I'm inspecting the current term stanza and existing `seeAlso` examples in `uberon-edit.obo`.","time":{"start":1778979534420,"end":1778979538163}}}
